        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/38366",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chrismsnz",
                        "name": "chrismsnz",
                        "displayName": "Chris Smith",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hi, I've run into this problem, too.\r\n\r\nThe above patch will fail with an error if a user tries to write to a syslog with no formatter.\r\n\r\nThere are two solutions:\r\n\r\n(1) Detect if there's a formatter set & use it if there is [chrismsnz-zf-syslog-format-1.patch]\r\n- Inconsistent with how the other writer's formatters are initialised\r\n\r\n(2) Set a default formatter (same approach as the other writers) [chrismsnz-zf-syslog-format-2.patch]\r\n- May need to override the default simple formatter string as it's probably not appropriate for syslog.\r\n\r\nApproach #2 is probably preferred.\r\n\r\nCheers,\r\nChris.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chrismsnz",
                        "name": "chrismsnz",
                        "displayName": "Chris Smith",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-02-08T14:45:46.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-02-08T14:45:46.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/38367",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chrismsnz",
                        "name": "chrismsnz",
                        "displayName": "Chris Smith",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Added patches referenced in the above comment",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=chrismsnz",
                        "name": "chrismsnz",
                        "displayName": "Chris Smith",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-02-08T14:46:24.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-02-08T14:46:24.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42633",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ramon",
                        "name": "ramon",
                        "displayName": "Ramon Henrique Ornelas",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Assigned to [~intiilapa]",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ramon",
                        "name": "ramon",
                        "displayName": "Ramon Henrique Ornelas",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-10-20T19:31:14.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-10-20T19:31:14.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/43672",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The reason we didn't provide formatter support originally is because you're using the syslog facility -- syslog() is expecting both a priority and a message as arguments, and usually indicates the priority in the log itself. Using the Simple formatter, we'd end up seeing the priority duplicated in such logs.\r\n\r\nAs such, patch 1 makes more sense -- if no formatter is present, simply use the current approach (syslog($priority, $message)), and if and only if a formatter has been explicitly provided, use it.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-12-17T11:39:32.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-12-17T11:39:32.000+0000"
                },
